# FormFactory: An Interactive Benchmarking Suite for Multimodal Form-Filling Agents ![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/formfactory-ai/formfactory/main/img/fig1v1_page_1.png)

   

## üìñ Overview Online form filling is one of the most common‚Äîyet most labor-intensive‚Äîdaily tasks. Traditional automation tools are usually rule-based scripts that struggle with complex and ever-changing web layouts. With the recent rise of Multimodal Large Language Models (**MLLMs**), researchers have begun to explore vision-language agents capable of "one-click" form completion. However, current models still fall short in layout understanding and field‚Äìvalue alignment. **FormFactory** bridges this gap by providing a high-fidelity benchmark and experimentation platform for multimodal form-filling agents. The project consists of: 1. üåê **Web Front-End** ‚Äì 40+ high-fidelity HTML forms from real-world scenarios spanning eight domains (academia, business, finance, healthcare, etc.). 2. üóÑ **Dataset** ‚Äì ‚Ä¢ `data1/` contains JSON **gold answers** (ground-truth field values) for each form. ‚Ä¢ `data2/` stores supporting **textual materials** that can be used as additional context or prompts. ‚Ä¢ `labeled-images/` provides page **screenshots** and corresponding **bbox annotations** (organized by folders A‚ÄìH). 3. ‚öôÔ∏è **Back-End Service** ‚Äì A lightweight Flask API that renders pages, receives submissions, and saves results automatically. 4. üìä **Evaluation Scripts** ‚Äì Utilities for computing field-level and form-level accuracy, layout reasoning metrics, and more. --- ## üöÄ Quick Start ### 1 Prerequisites - Python ‚â• 3.8 - Flask == 2.3.* - Install additional dependencies with:

## ‚ú® Key Features
- **Multi-Domain Coverage** ‚Äì Academia, business, arts, technology, finance, healthcare, law, and manufacturing.
- **High-Fidelity Pages** ‚Äì Realistic layouts to test visual understanding and field localization.
- **Dynamic Fields** ‚Äì Groups, repeatable sections, cascading dependencies, and more.
- **Interactive Evaluation** ‚Äì Run the server to observe model behavior in real time; results are saved automatically.
- **Easy to Extend** ‚Äì Add a new form by simply providing an HTML template and a JSON answer file.

```
